name: Music_590.wav
caption: This song features a male voice beatboxing. At the beginning of the song, he beatboxes a simple beat. Post that, the beatboxing is done in layers where the beat is one layer, the cymbals is another layer, a bass slide is another layer and a deep voice is the fourth layer. This is all done using the human voice and no instruments. This song is at a moderate tempo. This song can be played in a club.
